-- FACTBOX- Average pay at U.S. investment banks in 2013
-- 
-- Thu Jan 16, 2014 10:57AM EST
-- None



Jan 16 (Reuters) - Average pay at U.S. investment banks fell last year from a year before, although pay in retail banking and other areas rose.

